data.description: Welcome to 7234 Alicias Way, a stylish townhouse in Morrow, GA 30260, offering a perfect blend of modern and comfort. The well-appointed kitchen features stainless steel appliances, including a refrigerator, dishwasher, microwave, oven, and stove. The brown wooden cabinets provide ample storage space, complemented by elegant granite countertops. The large sitting dining area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. This townhouse boasts a spacious master bedroom that can comfortably accommodate king or queen-size beds. Two additional roomy bedrooms come with separate closets for convenient storage. The master bath is a relaxing retreat, featuring a shower and bath combo with modern fixtures and a simplistic layout. The laundry area is equipped to fit side-by-side washer and dryer units, with a built-in laundry rack for drying or storage. Tiled kitchen floors add a touch of sophistication, while plush carpeting throughout the living area and bedrooms enhances the overall comfort of this delightful home. Residents also enjoy the convenience of electric and Georgia Power for utilities, a homeowner association for community support, and access to a nearby park and dog park for outdoor enjoyment. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your forever home. Contact Chelsea to schedule a showing.
